                    "line_text": "Dans ton boudoir ne trouve accès ;",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 15,
                    "line_text": "Lise, abjure la tyrannie,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 16,
                    "line_text": "Pour le bonheur de tes sujets.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Combien les belles et les princes\nAiment l'abus d'un grand pouvoir !\nCombien d'amants et de provinces\nPoussés enfin au désespoir !\nCrains que la révolte ennemie\nDans ton boudoir ne trouve accès ;\nLise, abjure la tyrannie,\nPour le bonheur de tes sujets."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 3,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 17,
                    "line_text": "Par excès de coquetterie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 18,
                    "line_text": "Femme ressemble aux conquérants,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 19,
                    "line_text": "Qui vont bien loin de leur patrie",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 20,
                    "line_text": "Dompter cent peuples différents.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 21,
                    "line_text": "Ce sont de terribles coquettes !",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
