                    "line_text": "N'imite pas leurs vains projets.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 23,
                    "line_text": "Lise, ne fais plus de conquêtes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 24,
                    "line_text": "Pour le bonheur de tes sujets.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Par excès de coquetterie\nFemme ressemble aux conquérants,\nQui vont bien loin de leur patrie\nDompter cent peuples différents.\nCe sont de terribles coquettes !\nN'imite pas leurs vains projets.\nLise, ne fais plus de conquêtes,\nPour le bonheur de tes sujets."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 4,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 25,
                    "line_text": "Grâce aux courtisans pleins de zèle,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 26,
                    "line_text": "On approche des potentats",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 27,
                    "line_text": "Moins aisément que d'une belle",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 28,
                    "line_text": "Dont un jaloux suit tous les pas.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 29,
                    "line_text": "Mais sur ton lit, trône paisible,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 30,
                    "line_text": "Où le plaisir rend ses décrets,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 31,
                    "line_text": "Lise, sois toujours accessible,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 32,
                    "line_text": "Pour le bonheur de tes sujets.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Grâce aux courtisans pleins de zèle,\nOn approche des potentats\nMoins aisément que d'une belle\nDont un jaloux suit tous les pas.\nMais sur ton lit, trône paisible,\nOù le plaisir rend ses décrets,\nLise, sois toujours accessible,\nPour le bonheur de tes sujets."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 5,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 33,
                    "line_text": "Lise, en vain un roi nous assure",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 34,
                    "line_text": "Que, s'il règne, il le doit aux cieux,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 35,
                    "line_text": "Ainsi qu'à la simple nature",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 36,
                    "line_text": "Tu dois de charmer tous les yeux.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 37,
                    "line_text": "Bien qu'en des mains comme les tiennes",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 38,
                    "line_text": "Le sceptre passe sans procès,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 39,
                    "line_text": "De nous il faut que tu le tiennes,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 40,
                    "line_text": "Pour le bonheur de tes sujets.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Lise, en vain un roi nous assure\nQue, s'il règne, il le doit aux cieux,\nAinsi qu'à la simple nature\nTu dois de charmer tous les yeux.\nBien qu'en des mains comme les tiennes\nLe sceptre passe sans procès,\nDe nous il faut que tu le tiennes,\nPour le bonheur de tes sujets."
        },
        {
            "stanza_number": 6,
            "stanza_type": null,
            "lines": [
                {
                    "line_number": 41,
                    "line_text": "Pour te faire adorer sans cesse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 42,
                    "line_text": "Mets à profit ces vérités.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 43,
                    "line_text": "Lise, deviens bonne princesse,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "a"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 44,
                    "line_text": "Et respecte nos libertés.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "b"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 45,
                    "line_text": "Des roses que l'amour moissonne",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 46,
                    "line_text": "Ceins ton front tout brillant d'attraits,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 47,
                    "line_text": "Et garde long-temps ta couronne,",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "c"
                },
                {
                    "line_number": 48,
                    "line_text": "Pour le bonheur de tes sujets.",
                    "metrical_pattern": null,
                    "line_length": "8",
                    "rhyme": "d"
                }
            ],
            "stanza_text": "Pour te faire adorer sans cesse,\nMets à profit ces vérités.\nLise, deviens bonne princesse,\nEt respecte nos libertés.\nDes roses que l'amour moissonne\nCeins ton front tout brillant d'attraits,\nEt garde long-temps ta couronne,\nPour le bonheur de tes sujets."
